```plantuml
@startuml IBM_vpc-flowlogs-log-analysis

actor COS as User
participant "IBM Cloud Object Storage" as COS
participant "Handler.js" as Handler
participant "IBM Log Analysis API" as LogAnalysis
participant "Archive Bucket" as Archive

User -> COS: New Flow Log
COS -> Handler: Trigger Event
activate Handler

Handler -> COS: Retrieve Compressed Log
Handler -> Handler: Decompress Log
Handler -> Handler: Parse and Transform Log

Handler -> LogAnalysis: Forward Processed Log
activate LogAnalysis
LogAnalysis --> Handler: Acknowledgement
deactivate LogAnalysis

Handler -> Archive: Copy Processed Log
Handler -> COS: Delete Log from Receiver Bucket
deactivate Handler

@enduml
```